    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overview</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191020/extras/c8d7e14224ccb7ee89431b346091e53c.poster.avif?t=1767494034\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191020/extras/c8d7e14224ccb7ee89431b346091e53c.webm?t=1767494034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191020/extras/c8d7e14224ccb7ee89431b346091e53c.mp4?t=1767494034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >GU Fighters is an action roguelike where you unlock and upgrade new abilities after every round of combat. Play with up to 4 players locally or online to create your own unique build and be the first to win, or go solo/co-op to traverse varying environments and defeat hordes of enemies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Create your own unique build from over 200 unique unlockable abilities and upgrades over the course of a match, including abilities focused on close-range combat, projectiles, grappling, weapon usage, and more.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191020/extras/e8033c67ff8e670f5022d52287ef78a4.poster.avif?t=1767494034\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191020/extras/e8033c67ff8e670f5022d52287ef78a4.webm?t=1767494034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191020/extras/e8033c67ff8e670f5022d52287ef78a4.mp4?t=1767494034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Play locally or online with up to 4 players in intense, explosive rounds where anyone can win! Make risky moves to earn experience and gain new abilities, then play around your opponents' abilities to win the match.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191020/extras/8e6c376bde901cc03cf4914e133a3e4c.poster.avif?t=1767494034\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191020/extras/8e6c376bde901cc03cf4914e133a3e4c.webm?t=1767494034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191020/extras/8e6c376bde901cc03cf4914e133a3e4c.mp4?t=1767494034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Face off in one of over 50 unique maps where you may launch a foe to a new location at any moment. Use the best strategy possible for the current stage, anticipating and planning around any changes in location. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Experience a roguelike single-player or local/online co-op mode where you face off against hordes of enemies in various environments. Watch out for dangerous elite and boss fighters that may have their own abilities!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191020/extras/25f84caf5ef4dc04045535a16f2fad47.poster.avif?t=1767494034\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191020/extras/25f84caf5ef4dc04045535a16f2fad47.webm?t=1767494034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191020/extras/25f84caf5ef4dc04045535a16f2fad47.mp4?t=1767494034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Crisp, industry-standard rollback netcode in all multiplayer modes, ensuring the best possible experience for online gameplay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Hop into ranked mode and master your own style of gameplay!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch and bet on CPU vs CPU matches where you can customize your AI fighter's upgrades and abilities.</p></li></ul>",
